🔄 Unary Operators

| Operator | Name        | Example       | Output  |
| -------- | ----------- | ------------- | ------- |
| `+`      | Unary Plus  | `+5`          | `5`     |
| `-`      | Unary Minus | `-5`          | `-5`    |
| `++`     | Increment   | `++a` *(a=5)* | `6`     |
| `--`     | Decrement   | `--a` *(a=5)* | `4`     |
| `!`      | Logical NOT | `!true`       | `false` |
